Common VM configurations and launch scripts.

*.cfg - Xen vm configurations. Modify to match your own VMs
*.lxc - LXC container config scripts

MAC_INFO -
  MAC->IP mappings that are useful for Xen networking. Use libvirt networking
  utilities to set up DHCP with static MAC-IP assignments to have predictable
  per-VM IPs.
  Guide: http://serverfault.com/questions/627238/kvm-libvirt-how-to-configure-static-guest-ip-addresses-on-the-virtualisation-ho

